and 60.9% at EMMT and MMT clinics, respectively.The effect on EMMT retention was 
the same as that of MMT. Establishment of EMMT clinics was an effective strategy 
to expand the coverage of MMT and increase the retention of opiate dependents in 
the rural areas of the counties.

