Different risk factors between early and late cancer recurrences in patients 
without additional surgery after noncurative endoscopic submucosal dissection 
for early gastric cancer.

Yamada S(1), Hatta W(2), Shimosegawa T(2), Takizawa K(3), Oyama T(4), Kawata 
N(3), Takahashi A(4), Oka S(5), Hoteya S(6), Nakagawa M(7), Hirano M(8), Esaki 
M(9), Matsuda M(10), Nakaya N(11), Gotoda T(12).

Author information:
(1)Department of Gastroenterology and Hepatology, Japanese Red Cross Society 
Kyoto Daiichi Hospital, Kyoto, Japan.
(2)Division of Gastroenterology, Tohoku University Graduate School of Medicine, 
Sendai, Japan.
(3)Division of Endoscopy, Shizuoka Cancer Center, Shizuoka, Japan.
(4)Division of Endoscopy, Saku Central Hospital Advanced Care Center, Nagano, 
