(6)Department of Gastroenterology, Toranomon Hospital, Tokyo, Japan.
(7)Department of Endoscopy, Hiroshima City Hospital, Hiroshima, Japan.
(8)Department of Internal Medicine, Niigata Prefectural Central Hospital, 
