Cost-effectiveness analysis of hepatitis B vaccine booster in children born to 
HBsAg-positive mothers in rural China.

Wang Y(1), Shi JF(2), Wang L(3), Yan Y(4), Yao H(5), Dai M(6), Chen T(7), Qu 
C(8).

Author information:
(1)Immunology Department, National Cancer Center/National Clinical Research 
