Acute primary angle closure-treatment strategies, evidences and economical 
considerations.

Chan PP(1)(2), Pang JC(1), Tham CC(3)(4)(5).

Author information:
(1)Department of Ophthalmology & Visual Sciences, The Chinese University of Hong 
Kong, Hong Kong SAR, People's Republic of China.
(2)Hong Kong Eye Hospital, Kowloon, Hong Kong SAR, People's Republic of China.
(3)Department of Ophthalmology & Visual Sciences, The Chinese University of Hong 
Kong, Hong Kong SAR, People's Republic of China. clemtham@cuhk.edu.hk.
(4)Hong Kong Eye Hospital, Kowloon, Hong Kong SAR, People's Republic of China. 
clemtham@cuhk.edu.hk.
(5)Prince of Wales Hospital, Shatin, N.T., Hong Kong SAR, People's Republic of 
